Sheep & goats / 121 / 121 / 0 / 121 / 0

Outbreak 2: Bliznak, Malko Turnovo municipality, Burgas [For
location, see comment].
Date of start of the outbreak: 3 Apr 2011
Outbreak status: Continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: Village
Affected animals
