Cattle / 21 / 21 / 0 / 21 / 0
Sheep & goats / 121 / 121 / 0 / 121 / 0
Swine / 12 / 12 / 0 / 12 / 0

Summary of outbreaks
Total outbreaks: 2
Total animals affected
Species / Susceptible / Cases / Deaths / Destroyed / Slaughtered
Buffaloes / 72 / 72 / 0 / 72 / 0
Sheep & goats / 242 / 242 / 0 / 242 / 0
Cattle / 21 / 21 / 0 / 21 / 0
Swine / 12 / 12 / 0 / 12 / 0

Epidemiology
Source of the outbreak(s) or origin of infection: Unknown or
inconclusive

Control measures
Measures applied: Control of wildlife reservoirs, Stamping out,
Quarantine, Movement control inside the country, Zoning, Disinfection
of infected premises/establishment(s).
No vaccination, No treatment of affected animals.

Measures to be applied: No other measures

Diagnostic test results
Laboratory name and type: FMD National Reference Laboratory (National
laboratory)
