Buffaloes / antibody detection ELISA / 3 Apr 2011 / Positive
Buffaloes / Non-structural protein ELISA / 3 Apr 2011 / Positive
Sheep & goats / antibody detection ELISA / 3 Apr 2011 / Positive
Sheep & goats / Non-structural protein ELISA / 3 Apr 2011 / Positive

